com.io7m.jspatial.octtrees

Interface OctTreeSDType<T extends OctTreeMemberType<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The precise type of octtree members.
    All Superinterfaces:
    OctTreeType<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OctTreeSDBasic, OctTreeSDLimit, OctTreeSDPrune, OctTreeSDPruneLimit

    public interface OctTreeSDType<T extends OctTreeMemberType<T>>
extends OctTreeType<T>

    The interface provided by octtree implementations that distinguish between static (immovable) and dynamic (movable) objects.

    • Method Detail

      • octTreeInsertSD

        boolean octTreeInsertSD(T item,
                        SDType type)
        Insert the object item into the octtree. The object will be given the categorization type.

        The function returns false if the object could not be inserted for any reason (perhaps due to being too large).

        Parameters:
        item - The object to insert
        type - The categorization of the object
        Returns:
        true if the object was inserted

      • octTreeSDClearDynamic

        void octTreeSDClearDynamic()
        Remove all dynamic (movable) objects from the tree.
